  "instructions": [
    "Heat the coconut oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the sliced onions and sauté for 5 minutes, until softened.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the Jamaican curry powder and Bhuna paste, and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the fish fillets and cook for 3-4 minutes, until lightly browned.",
    "Pour in the lime juice and stir to coat the fish.",
    "Add a pinch of salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Simmer the curry for 5-7 minutes, until the fish is cooked through.",
    "Garnish with mixed greens and sliced green chilies.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
